PATENT NOTICE
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

One or more inventions disclosed in this repository are the subject of a
pending United States patent application:

  Title:    Privacy Governance and Cryptographic Consent Enforcement System
  Filed:    February 23, 2026
  Status:   Provisional application pending

Protected components include but are not limited to:

  - Cryptographic Consent Token (CCT) generation, signing, and verification
  - Privacy Governance Engine (Bouncer) — automated consent enforcement
  - Invisibility Ledger — tamper-evident consent audit trail
  - State-Persistence Monitor — post-revocation data detection
  - Removal Payload Engine (RPE) — automated legal deletion enforcement

All patent rights are reserved. Nothing in this repository shall be construed
as granting, by implication, estoppel, or otherwise, any license under any
patent, patent application, or other intellectual property right of Adworth.

